{"type": "article", "id": 5496, "title": "LO-LO 厨柜", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-23T07:31:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052339420NamZ4FDHfp9QgT8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t办公室不同于家居空间，那怎样的厨柜才适合于办公空间呢？两位设计师 Tanya Repina 与 Misha Repin 带来了他们的解决方案 LO-LO。这是一个个性化的胶囊状厨柜，内部不同的模块可以满足包括茶叶、咖啡、勺子、叉子等的储存需求，亦有挂置杯子的内立面设计与放置茶壶与咖啡机的水平搁板设计，一款中空结构的 LO-LO 甚至可以将微波炉直接嵌进去，合理利用空间。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233940xWFrJNdwtn1YT025.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052339408eticHkWxmoyL3g2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233941sxqOtAuQF5johfBX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.653125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233941RZM9PLjlmw73V4uo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.653125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233942wF5bCqsZDIN0LGXY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7828125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}